{"tid":592485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本擬將成人定義下調至18歲","createTime":"2018-03-14T08:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T09:03:12.000Z","uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0cd073e2b05443983a979a1653633d22838eef","tid":592485,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/SIG=28p7ofc/30493553325a6a4f7265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2FSIG%3D28p7ofc%2F30493553325a6a4f7265.jpg&h=5258a5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據日本共同社報道，日本政府擬修改法律，將成人年齡定義從20歲下調至18歲，女性結婚年齡將從16歲上調至18歲，與男性相同。若法案獲得通過，由明治時代起持續至今的「成人」定義將發生變化。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府爭取2022年4月1日使成人年齡下調生效，到時飲酒、吸煙以及賽馬等有年齡限制的相關法律須作出修改。<br />\n<br />\n至於統一結婚年齡，由於結婚最低年齡與成人年齡將相同，未成年人結婚需得到父母同意的《民法》條款將被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n此外，法案通過後，年滿18歲將無需父母同意下可簽訂合同，由於擔心有商家以不良手法唆使，政府將立法規定「困惑情況下簽訂的合同」可予以撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1788227/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A9%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E8%87%B318%E6%AD%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1788227%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E8%2587%25B318%25E6%25AD%25B2&d=GCF33%2Fs%2F6JqYT7mrWSgHcQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=b5ac533e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1788227/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A9%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E8%87%B318%E6%AD%B2</a>"},{"pid":"8fdf0ec07432ffced69b0c4848b91eb6d5b7296c","tid":592485,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"今次日服官方改版唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a5ee6cc94ff50fb63d5c72fc7127c114969c60","tid":592485,"uid":65346,"like":0,"disli